Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pieces of shit in \Nthis castle are a blight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will carve them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tear them out by the roots...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go through everything,\Nincluding documents and maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:09.31,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 6\NMen of Destiny"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss anything, not even scribbles.\NWe're taking everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You really did... \Ntake over the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here you are, Olmi-Boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have the \Nenergy to argue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give in, it will \Nbe the end of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the Father of Orte,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the founder of the Orte Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that about sixty years ago,\Nhe appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have yet to find out whether he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,belonged to the Drifters or the Ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, he showed up at the bar and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instigated people to rise against government.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his compelling speeches and ability
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to capture the hearts \Nand minds of the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he initiated the rebellion\Nand marched on the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the record left
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at that time, he acted as if \Nhe were an "expert demagogue."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after he founded Orte,\Nhe suddenly committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason behind his \Nsuicide remains unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was a Drifter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you happen to know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with that mustache?!\NIs he messing with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobunaga, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyo dragged the soldiers to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about carving them up\Nand tearing them out by the roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What... the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Toyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How righteous are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, what does he mean by\N"tearing them out by the roots"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He means to "slaughter them all."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From looking at the male Elves, you should
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be able to tell their females \Nare also good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been kidnapping\Nthose women regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been an easy guess\Nthose soldiers would rape them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've known better even\Nbefore we took down this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should not carve them up\Nor tear them out by the roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing is my \Njob in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just be yourself,\Nbeing all honest and straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the twisted and warped jobs to\Nthe Demon King of the Sixth Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anything but my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what will happen to you all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If our government ever finds out\Nabout this, you'll be all slaughtered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been abusing these \Nwomen all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would be making a big mistake\Nif you think you can leave here alive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by just laying down your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were determined to exterminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it would be logical that\Nit's your turn to be exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die. Die and reincarnate into black powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St-Stop. Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! You've been\Nabusing us all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's your turn, you're seriously\Nbegging us for your lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've just transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St-Sto... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I hit you pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Satsuma boys are very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took care of those soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice sight, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids are too young \Nto take command of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me. Don't be reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands have been dirty for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isenagashima, Enryaku-ji on Mt. Hiei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Azai and Asakura clans...\Numm... I can't even count...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn how many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about any of that!\NThat's not my concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back. What's going on?\NAre you two fighting? Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no? If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since someone\Npunched me and yelled at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not since my father did. I miss that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, there was also my tutor, Hirate...\NHe rebuked me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was older than my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never... slept with a woman before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept insisting he hadn't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we killed him, we would be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olmi-Boobs! Let him play with your boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cut their heads \Noff and pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much we hated them,\Nthey all became souls after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use their bodies for black powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor about the Drifters spread
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,throughout the surrounding \Nvillages in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drifters Rescue Elven Village\Nand Attack Occupying Magistrate."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after the female Elves \Nconfined at the lord's castle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,returned to their villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the confusion about the rumor\Nturned into the assurance of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, those women returned with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the scrupulous "gifts" sent by Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a "Proclamation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The content was classic Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It touched readers' hearts \Nbut manipulated their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you want to have your own state?\NThen, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to hand \Nover your women yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a newly appointed magistrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let them be used \Nas playthings once more?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also wrote a memorandum that\Nproved how Orte has reached its limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attaching the contents of the document\Ncollected from the magistrate's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a jerk to pull a trick like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subsequently, the Elf villages began\Nrising in revolt one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.51,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Elven Revolts Spread"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elves are breaking away\Nfrom Orte's subjugation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's is going \Non?! That idiot Murasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... Who... Who gives\Na damn about Drifters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are losing on the eastern\Nand western fronts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the mysterious \Nforce in the far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the Elves are rising up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, this empire is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The status of the war \Ncontinues to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, we don't have enough\Nforces to fight this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been engaged in war for forty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've even been transferring soldiers\Nin from the remote territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supplies are running short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tax revenue and seized assets from mainland
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and occupied territories\Nare both about to run dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we consider a peaceful solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Father's idea that\Nthe empire was never to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It became the national policy.\NNo way we can give in that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry I am late. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you all waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Count Saint-Germi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am late, so late. I got caught up with\Nan unexpected incident right before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those twinkies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hears you, you never \Nknow what he'll do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is that Count Saint-Germi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! H-Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a powerful aristocrat\Nwho owns a quarter of the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Father founded the country,\Nhe was the first aristocrat to defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been said the Orte Empire could\Nnot have existed without his betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, no one has\Nbeen able to stand up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has never taken up arms in war.\NHe is free to live as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said he helped Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that fifty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ancient is... that old twinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my apology for being tardy,\NI have something interesting to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a quite surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are aware of our naval fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that transports supplies to the\Nbattlefields in the west, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have something to take this down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to write with, quickly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, please use my lipstick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, use mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Give it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I repeatedly inquire\Nof you whether or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this supply route is practical?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fleet has been seized and sunk\Nto the bottom of the ocean by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another ship has been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They're going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another got hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those merchants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn merchant guild of Gu Binnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We provide home delivery\Nservice with the mark of Griffon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Shylock Co. of the Gu Binnen Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen of Orte,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how do you like the Gu Binnen\Nspecialty mix of fish oil and animal fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat your fill, you jackasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this a gift to your\Ncountry's mustached Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora! Tora! Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, what is this "Tora, Tora, Tora"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Admiral taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to yell that after a \Nsuccessful surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora! Tora! Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora! Tora! Tora! Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we won this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.63,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"June 6, 1942\NYamaguchi Tamon\NImperial Japanese Navy Admiral"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be payback for the fights we\Ninstigated in all the neighboring states.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we shouldn't have made an
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enemy of the merchant guild of the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, there are rebellions\Nin the occupied territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Elves have risen in revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, we are talking about Elves,\Naren't we? How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can handle them!\NThey are just serf uprisings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pressing matter is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the situation in the west...\Nwithout due consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.04,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, they are hopeless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orte expanded its territories by\Nsuccessively attacking the neighboring lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that soon we won't\Njust be dealing with the Elven revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their revolt will amplify the wrath\Nof the other races until it boils over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebellion will spread\Nthroughout the territories like wildfire
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and roar into a festival of revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is inevitable for this\Nmovement to expand westward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the west, where most of our\Ntroops are on duty, will be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! This country is in checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered I have\Nurgent business to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, good luck with the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are leaving. No time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to steal that lamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the painting over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the Elven rebel army immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I heard that the Drifters\Nwere involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I will do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Are you talking about\Nthose Elves? I want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are from Fizona Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Shara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't rise up now,\Nwe shouldn't be calling ourselves Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others are steadily flowing in to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can win this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that Drifters sparked\Nthis whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to answer that. Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though those Drifters rescued you,\Nafter all, they are not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they just humans with "short ears"?\NAre they trustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are! At least to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.28,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Grumble, grumble, grumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to calm down.\NYou're a full-grown man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the Minister of the Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so angry in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide on the\Nvillage head council system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have gradually risen to power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have become a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about strategy\Nand those sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to understand intrigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu, you may be able to totally\Ndiscern what they are thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you cannot read their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know for a fact that \Nthe Elves will follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could become a king or \Nanything I want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but without a doubt, someday they\Nwould turn their bows against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day at some temple, we'd wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to find ourselves surrounded by fire arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you repeat Honno-ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read people's hearts, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through enough revolts already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you betrayed that many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... Twice by my\Nyounger brother Nobukatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:14.40,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Errr uhh"\N"Grind grind"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,twice by the Katsuie and Hayashi clans,\NAzai, and Matsunaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Araki, Hatano, Bessho, Mitsuhide, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once I've made a decision on something,\NI won't stop until I get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing with the \Ndirt from the toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work cautiously, or else\Nyou could get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the other villagers to bring
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lots and lots of dirt from \Nthe toilets and sheds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does he like shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked blacksmiths in \Nall the villages, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I expected, they all told me\Nit would be too hard to replicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those blacksmiths in Sakai and Kunitomo\Nreally had excellent craftsmanship after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think can make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, the expert blacksmiths\Nof the Dwarves could...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing they are good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dwarves"... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the archery coach for you Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nasu Suketaka Yoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to train your lazy asses so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:30.44,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter, mutter, mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't even be able to cry or laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yell, "Hurray! Minamoto clan!"\Nbefore and after you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.69,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Muahahaha"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamoto clan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now begin intensive training...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to make 10,000 shots\Nout of 100, not 100 shots out of 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. Hurray! Minamoto clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he jokes around, he looks like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when he is serious,\Nhe has a dreadful beauty, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is too good to be a "Short Ear."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not sure why you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the youngest of eleven brothers\Nof the Nasu clan, yet I am the ugliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even describe the\Nbeauty of my brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere beauty walks,\Nflowers blossom on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ocean splits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gold falls from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call true beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is absolutely not true.\NHurray! Minamoto clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sasshu swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put all your strength \Nand heart into one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss him or he dodges, what then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die without hesitation.\NIt's an advancement to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't teach the Elves my swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they are cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are excellent with a bow.\NThey are like God-sent archers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, the blacksmiths \Nin the village... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have such an eerie feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming near.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling I have... \NIt's not the Orte's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell Sekigahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the nauseating smell of a bloody battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Gilles de Rais.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them, the Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill those Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blight the fig trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before they bear fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ghost Sorcery"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Androgynous Woman"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Olminu of Stone Coffins"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 7\NChaos Diver"
